DISTRICT #95 SUPT. BOOTH'S FINAL WEEK DISPATCH

Supt. Daniel Booth gives his final school year dispatch, sharing about:
* the final meal of the school year this Friday;
* a summer meal plan starting June 1 and running through July, continuing on Monday-Wednesday-Friday and being expanded into the community;
* Teacher Appreciation yard signs;
* CMS 8th Grade Promotion Video Salute and teacher-staff celebratory parade by students' homes this Thursday.

#CES95Proud
#ILSchoolsStepUp
